sequenceDiagram
  participant D as Donor
  participant S as ChariSmart
  participant A as Admin
  participant R as NGO/Orphanage
  participant V as Volunteer
  D->>S: Submit food donation
  R->>S: Submit food request
  A->>S: Approve donation and request
  S->>S: Calculate match score
  A->>S: Assign volunteer
  S->>V: Send pickup/delivery assignment
  V->>S: Mark picked up
  V->>S: Mark delivered
  R->>S: Confirm delivery and rating
  S->>D: Notify completion
